SUMMARY:An Evening with Gabor Mate: The Myth of Normal
DTSTAMP:20260406T013616Z
DTSTART:20260414T023000Z
DESCRIPTION:Embark on a profound journey into the intricate landscapes of t
	he human mind and soul with renowned physician\, speaker\, and bestselling
	 author\, Dr. Gabor Maté.\n\nhttps://www.seattlecenter.com/events/event-ca
	lendar/an-evening-with-gabor-mate-the-myth-of-normal
